data.description: Check out this 3 bedroom possibly 4 bedroom ranch home on a 1 acre Cul-de-sac lot. This home features 3 main floor bedrooms and 1 1/2 baths. An attached 2 stall garage, main floor laundry, and open concept floor plan are just a few of the bonuses you'll find. The kitchen includes appliances and has a slider off of the eating area leading you to a rear deck that overlooks the wooded backyard.  The finished basement provides ample storage along with a huge rec room and an office that could easily be modified and used as a 4th bedroom. Minutes away from Crane's and Fenn Valley and 13 minutes away from Holland. With a touch of TLC you could make this house your home.
